         <exercise workspace="2.0in">
            <p>
                A bank account has a balance of –$45 (money owed). A deposit of $30 is made. What is the new balance?
            </p>
         </exercise>
         <exercise workspace="2.0in">
            <p>
                An elevator starts on floor –3 (three floors below ground). It goes up 8 floors. What floor does the elevator stop on?

            </p>
